[Over the past 7 years ProMED has focused on foodborne transmission of Chagas disease. Based on the present data it is not possible to know how much is traditional transmission by triatomid bugs, which role congenital transmission has, and if oral transmission is also involved. ProMED will be happy to post more details of the outbreak. - Mod.EP

